name: Portrait Session
description:
Engagements, Bridals, Maternity, Birth, Newborn, Children, Family, HS Senior.

*All sessions include 1-2 hours at location of your choice, 40-50 edited images, and photographers print release & disc. Refer a friend for a complimentary 11x14 print.

*An additional location or use of the blue couch is $25. 

*Announcements and card designs are $40.

*Travel expense for locations in Cedar City & Mesquite are $25. Las Vegas $50. Salt Lake City $100. California & surrounding states please contact me for traveling and accommodation expenses.

*Tax is required for all sessions, services and products.

name: Albums, Prints & Gifts
description:
*For complete Print items and Pricing please see my blog at:  http://elorephoto.blogspot.com/p/contact.html

*For client orders please allow 2 days for your print order and amount to be posted in the drop down menu at:
http://elorephoto.bigcartel.com/product/8x8-storyboard-print
 
*8x8 Storyboard Print is printed on photo paper and then adhered onto the canvas. Choose one photo or four to place in design. Stand is included in gold or black. Shipping for 8x8 Storyboard Print is an additional $4. Please select 8x8 Storyboard Print WITH Shipping if you need it mailed and please remember to Include the name & address for the canvas to be mailed to.

*Tax is required for all sessions, services and products.

name: Wedding Packages
description:
